name: The PeaceMakers - 25hr Party People - MetaMusicVideo
description:
The music video to our song 25Hr Party People.  

What happens when the lockdown is unlocked?

Could this be the first music video filmed entirely in the metavserse?  Could it be the second? Maybe, maybe not....

Filmed on location at our purpose built film studio in Cryptovoxels metaverse.  

Come visit the film stage; https://www.cryptovoxels.com/play?coords=E@721E,395N
